In terms of specifications  all same. But there are 2 types. Spec and Revo. Spec 1/2/3 uses carburettor and CDI and the engine has liquid and air cooling  Revo 1/2/3(LED) uses EFI and ECU and the engine is has liquid cooling.

Spec 1/2 uses older design tailboard and fairing. Spec 3/Revo 1 share the same tailboards and parts but engine differs. Revo 2/3(LED) uses newer split tailboard design but Revo 2 uses Halogen headlight and taillight  Revo 3(LED) uses  of course  LED headlight.
But all have VTEC. Difference between the Spec and Revos are the legal exhaust.
Spec can use all the Spec legal exhaust. Revo have different one cus they connect differently.
